  uses the =fileQueue= service to remove the file from the queue so
  the stale filename doesn't linger.
- New Remove button next to Upload lets users drop their selection
  without a page refresh.
- Per-instance =@queueName= so multiple forms on a page (or across
  routes) don't collide on a global "resumes" queue name.

