[2026-04-22/23 frontend] Shipped:
- Drag-install bookmarklet on =/job-posts/new/paste= (href set
  imperatively via =on-insert= to bypass Ember's =unsafe:javascript=
  sanitizer).
- MV3 browser extension =career-caddy-sender= at
  =/extensions/career-caddy-sender-0.2.5.{zip,xpi}=. Popup shows
  installed version in the top-right, remembers origin/auto-submit/
  auto-score preferences per browser.
- Auto-submit: extension URL =?auto=1= → paste form fills, submits,
  polls scrape to completion.
- Auto-score: =?score=1= implies auto=1; after scrape completes, paste
  transitions to =/job-posts/:id/scores?auto=1= and the scores
  controller auto-triggers career-data scoring (or opens existing
  completed career-data score when one exists).
- Application-route global =message= listener stashes to
  =sessionStorage= so bookmarklet payloads survive a login redirect.
- Install docs on the paste page split into three platform cards
  (Firefox temporary / persistent / Chrome-family) with warning on
  temp-install state loss.
Shipped via PRs #58 and #60 (frontend), #41 and #45 (api — dedup
branching + pydantic-ai 'openai:' prefix strip), parent bumps #21
and #25.

