[2026-04-18 api+frontend] Branches:
=feature/job-post-reextract= (api), =feature/job-post-paste-edit=
(frontend + parent).
- Paste page (=/job-posts/paste=): optional URL input above the
  textarea. URL submission redirects to =/job-posts/scrape= with
  =?url== query param so the existing browser-scrape flow takes over.
- Edit page (=/job-posts/{id}/edit=): "Re-extract from paste" textarea
  + button. Calls =POST /api/v1/job-posts/{id}/reextract/= which
  runs the AI extractor on pasted text and merges non-None fields
  onto the existing JobPost. Company is intentionally preserved.
  Persists a Scrape with =job_post= linked for provenance. 7 tests.
- Future: 3rd submission mode on paste (URL+text together) would POST
  to =from-text/= with both =text= and =link= so the JobPost gets the
  URL as link and the parser fills the rest. Not wired yet.

