* SHIPPED MCP slim-response refactor — YAML + TOOL_SHAPES audit :ai:mcp:
:PROPERTIES:
:ARCHIVE_TIME: 2026-04-29 Wed 10:49
:ARCHIVE_FILE: ~/Network/syncthing/Projects/career_caddy/todo.org
:ARCHIVE_OLPATH: Inbox
