Root cause was failure mode #2: =ApplicationPromptBuilder.build()=
appended =injected_prompt= LAST under a =## Additional Instructions=
header, AFTER a default preamble whose leading "OUTPUT FORMAT — strictly
plain text" rules outweighed it on every LLM tested.

Fix in =api/job_hunting/lib/services/application_prompt_builder.py=:
move =injected_prompt= to the TOP of the prompt under a "User
Instructions (PRIORITY — these override the default behavior and output
format guidance below)" header, and reword the default preamble's
format clause to defer to the user override. Tests in
=tests/test_application_prompt_builder.py= lock the ordering invariant.

