* TODO SHIPPED application-flow sankey: circular link crash from misread-status corrections
CLOSED: [2026-05-20]
:PROPERTIES:
:ARCHIVE_TIME: 2026-05-20 Wed 09:11
:ARCHIVE_FILE: ~/Network/syncthing/Projects/career_caddy/todo.org
